				<wikidot:authorName>Henzoid</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5190300</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p style="text-align: center;">Beans beans they're good for your heart</p> <p style="text-align: center;">The more you eat, the more you fart</p> <p style="text-align: center;">The more you fart, the worse the scent</p> <p style="text-align: center;">Which is why we need Lord Jethusent</p> <hr /> <p>Before anyone asks&#8230; yes, I did go out and buy a clock, fill it with baked beans, and use it for this SCP.</p> <p><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/henzoids-author-page" target="_blank">Also, I have an author page now!</a></p> <hr /> <p>AAAAAAAAAA HOW DID THIS HIT 100 IT'S A BEANS SHITPOST</p> <p>Okay, it's not a shitpost, but it's still about beans. God, this was my first SCP ever, and now, 7 months later, it hits 100. Dang. Thanks y'all.</p> 
				 	]]>
